---

import unah from '../assets/images/unah-sellos.png';
---

<section id="first-steps" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative bg-[#0d1117] section">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-white text-center">
        <span class="text-[#58a6ff]">#</span> Mis primeros pasos en la tecnología
      </h2>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline line -->
        <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-[#30363d] transform md:translate-x-[-0.5px]"></div>
        
        <!-- Timeline item 1 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:justify-between mb-16">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] md:text-right md:pr-8 order-2 md:order-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Victor Reparations</h3>
            <p class="text-[#8b949e]">
              Fundé una pequeña iniciativa de reparación y venta de computadoras para poder costear mis estudios.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#161b22] border-4 border-[#58a6ff] rounded-full transform md:translate-x-[-50%] z-10 flex items-center justify-center order-1 md:order-2 mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <span class="text-[#58a6ff] text-xs font-bold">01</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] md:pl-8 order-3">
            <div class="bg-[#161b22] border border-[#30363d] rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-[#58a6ff] transition-colors">
              <div class="w-full h-auto rounded mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="35" fill="#58a6ff" />
                  <path d="M50 20 V35 M50 65 V80 M20 50 H35 M65 50 H80" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="10" fill="white" />
                </svg>

                <h1 class="text-white text-3xl font-bold">
                  <span class="text-[#58a6ff]">Victor</span> Reparations
                </h1>
                

              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Timeline item 2 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:justify-between">
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] md:pr-8 order-2">
            <div class="bg-[#161b22] border border-[#30363d] rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-[#58a6ff] transition-colors">
              <img 
                src={unah.src} 
                alt="UNAH" 
                class="w-full h-auto rounded mb-3"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#161b22] border-4 border-[#58a6ff] rounded-full transform md:translate-x-[-50%] z-10 flex items-center justify-center order-1 mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <span class="text-[#58a6ff] text-xs font-bold">02</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] md:text-left md:pl-8 order-3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Becario en la UNAH</h3>
            <p class="text-[#8b949e]">
              Tuve la fortuna de ser becario en el Departamento de TI de la Universidad Nacional Autónoma de Honduras. Cada cable conectado, cada sistema reparado, era un paso hacia mi sueño.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-[#58a6ff] pl-4 italic text-lg md:text-xl text-[#c9d1d9] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          "No fue fácil. Pero cada obstáculo superado me acercaba más a mi meta."
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-[#bc8cff] rounded-full filter blur-[150px] opacity-10 parallax" data-speed="0.2"></div>
</section>
